 * THIS FILE WAS GENERATED BY THE STREAMIX TOOL `smxtrsp`. DO NOT EDIT THIS
 * FILE EDIT THE ORIGINAL STREAMIX-SOURCE FILE `<app_name>.smx` INSTEAD!
